  "detailed_description": "\"Jellyfish Season\" is a very short visual novel. The parable tells about people trying to find themselves in life. You have to play for a fat man named Niklas, who meets a strange girl on the tropical beach. She writes poetry and says that she is ... dead.<br />\r\nThere is no choices in the game. Only one beach. One girl. Lots of jellyfish.",
